Keep Working While Your Records Download with Background Priming (Beta)

Now when you download records for offline use, that process happens in the background and you can continue using your mobile device uninterrupted. The app notifies you when the download is complete and youâ€™re ready to work offline.

This change applies to the Salesforce Mobile App Plus for iOS and Android on phone and tablets in all editions, except Database.com.

Mobile Offline is available in orgs with the Salesforce Mobile App Plus license and to users within that org who have the Mobile Offline for Salesforce Mobile App Plus user permission.

To participate in this beta program, contact your customer success representative or account executive.
title: Background Priming for Salesforce Mobile App
